 Performance benchmarking: Explicit vs Implicit Transactions 

		 
			Posted on  July 27, 2011  by  Amit Banerjee 		 
	 
		 Benchmarking… The single most important word in Performance Tuning. Without an established benchmark, you really don’t know when to actually call it a day! 
